{"tid":1504343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到今時今日，香港人唯一出路！","createTime":"2019-08-25T09:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T10:21:48.000Z","uid":193663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d84e8f0187e776b260d38b3dfab61a4d663a650","tid":1504343,"uid":193663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"今時今日明顯剩係中聯辦同埋機場先會令政府緊張，搞咁多區分晒人力，個個分晒心，不如集中錫春袋！<br />\n<br />\n入機場三大好處<br />\n<br />\n1.機場最能夠影響香港經濟<br />\n2.機場入邊，警渣唔用得催淚彈或者槍，誤傷遊客，死都唔得掂<br />\n3.近身肉搏先最能夠將人數優勢發揮出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n警渣突然發出不反對通知書！居心叵測！<br />\n另外本人用呢個名極之少見，又咁啱有MTR職員指人冒認！司馬昭之心 路人皆知！<br />\n<br />\n今日封三個地鐵站、出催淚彈、橡膠子彈、水炮車。<br />\n擺明係一早部署好！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人！<br />\nTHE HONG KONG WAY IS NOT ONLY A SLOGAN OR A GAME! IT IS THE TRUE AND ONLY HONG KONG WAY! <br />\n聽日！<br />\n機場見！</span>"},{"pid":"29951241bacccd7c1cfe11f8037d2be7b649842d","tid":1504343,"uid":193663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:59:16.000Z","msg":"唔係要𡨭人對錯！<br />\n但香港人！<br />\n醒下啦！<br />\n機場先係終極目標啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家啲狗不斷提升武力<br />\n我地呢？<br />\n巿民一早慣左tear gas 橡膠子彈 甚至布袋彈<br />\n仲唔入機場？等幾時啊？</span></span>"},{"pid":"e93fd0eae544f68c7f7e0e24caaf32439e736a51","tid":1504343,"uid":193663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:01:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係指責<br />\n但尋日今日光復左啲咩？<br />\n報左咩仇？<br />\n點解咁大個春袋<br />\n我可只要塞路已經可以<br />\n咁易做都唔做？</span></span>"},{"pid":"cef59b1f88c4071723f0602811f81080c481eca7","tid":1504343,"uid":193663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"自推一下<br />\n大家都幫手推！"},{"pid":"40162bde0a1bd4135d364af3768abbc4e2b277c6","tid":1504343,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2b40bcc0a9cc1a95314cf3cd45c8cbae034ea55","tid":1504343,"uid":193663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:16:27.000Z","msg":"無出去嘅<br />\n入機場啦！"},{"pid":"d6d5fdc472af6f7787023dbe57f5d664990f8605","tid":1504343,"uid":193663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:21:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入機場！救手足！<br />\n無事咪當遊下車河囉</span></span>"}]}